This distribution is a CPAN bundle for Perl-Critic and related
modules.  It does not contain any code.  Rather, it just contains a
magical list of modules that the CPAN.pm utility knows how to deal
with.  To install, give this command:

  perl -MCPAN -e 'install Bundle::Perl::Critic'

